quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32543,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/28\/seek-refuge-vices-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2996,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from vices, trials, and oppression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from disability, sloth, cowardice, senility, and miserliness. I seek refuge in You from the torment of the grave and from the trials of life and death.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38379,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/refuge-many-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2996,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from many evil trials","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from the trials and punishment of the Hellfire, from the trials and punishment of the grave, from the evil of the trials of wealth, and from the evil of the trials\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/05\/refuge-fitnah-dajjal\/","url_meta":{"origin":2996,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Seek refuge from tribulations, torment of grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this nation will be put to trial in their graves. Were it not that you would stop burying each other, I would have called upon Allah to make you hear the punishment of the grave as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":778,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/13\/better-to-avoid-fitnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2996,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Avoiding trials better than rushing into them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"There will come tribulations in which one sitting will be better than one standing. The one standing will be better than one walking. The one walking will be better than one running. Whoever seeks these tribulations\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2575,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/29\/seek-refuge-after-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":2996,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for refuge at the end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt